{"tid":917872,"cid":21,"subCid":1,"title":"林夕、黃偉文、周耀輝","createTime":"2018-11-26T17:41:40.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-07T10:32:27.000Z","uid":158749,"like":54,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"4b648b663c132f61b9b0f917e94a65f988533e10","tid":917872,"uid":158749,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-26T17:41:40.000Z","msg":"林夕說：「如果用3種東西比喻我們，我是一塊海綿，黃偉文是一個刺蝟，周耀輝是一個雕塑，而且是紫檀木的，小葉紫檀，最貴那種，現在已經滅絕了。」<br />\n<br />\n拋吓磚先:<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n麥浚龍《借火》<br />\n剛剛要去便利店裡為著香煙無人點火湊巧你正走出路上搖搖盪盪明明喊過不借得太多也想借點火<br />\n<br />\n後來周耀輝同林夕合作係麥浚龍一人寫三首合左隻故事出黎，叫《天生地夢》。去到《問世 evil is a point of view》，直頭大家合作寫詞寫左個故事出黎。<br />\n<br />\n仲有好多寫俾黃耀明／達明一派既歌都好正。<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過周耀輝好少人提<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a5a1bee0e975fa61e5a0507a8a6d000396ae7a8e","tid":917872,"uid":36142,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-26T17:47:07.000Z","msg":"雌雄同體<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9bbf0c1f65bc351fdf1614a53963d4840a7a81a9","tid":917872,"uid":213656,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-26T18:13:58.000Z","msg":"借火真係好癲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"101e1835800df706849b11b2dd4297ae6b7ab99c","tid":917872,"uid":156010,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-26T18:23:46.000Z","msg":"無念隻碟都好正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b8312a0b7c2cde4d7c8f79297d1f9bd50205ef72","tid":917872,"uid":179935,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-26T18:28:45.000Z","msg":"陳詠謙是屎"},{"pid":"e11ba9b681945744c9c75a5b8fc7a54827b9cdb1","tid":917872,"uid":43159,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-26T18:53:29.000Z","msg":"死先死先死先死先死先死先<br />\n